stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> ResultCreated
    ResultCreated --> SavedRun : auto_save_experiments = true
    ResultCreated --> TransientRun : guest or autosave off

    TransientRun --> SavedRun : save_display_files
    TransientRun --> SavedRun : sync selection
    SavedRun --> TransientRun : unsave_display_files
    SavedRun --> TransientRun : sync selection

    SavedRun --> SavedRun : clean preview and preprocess assets
    TransientRun --> Deleted : retention cutoff exceeded
    TransientRun --> Deleted : explicit delete or cancel

    note right of SavedRun
      SegmentedImage.user is the
      authenticated account
    end note

    note right of TransientRun
      Results remain accessible in the
      current session but are eligible
      for later cleanup
    end note

    Deleted --> [*]

